languages.text: "Чутье подсказываем мне, что дворец — узловая точка в рейде противника. Наши вокс-инженеры регистрируют сигналы неизвестной природы, идущие из вашей резиденции в другие точки планеты — полагаю, в здании находится контрольный пункт этих мразей. Сможем выбить командование — ослабим силы на периферии".

"I have a feeling that the palace is the anchor point of the enemy's raid. Our vox engineers are registering unknown signals coming from your residence to other areas on the planet — the scum must have set up a control centre inside. We take out their command — and we'll weaken their peripheral forces."

languages.text: 「宮殿は敵の襲撃基点になるような気がします。ヴォクス工兵隊があなたの住居からこの惑星の他の地域に発信される未知のシグナルを観測しています―宮殿内に制御室を設置したのでしょう。奴らの司令部を破壊すれば―周辺部隊を弱体化させることができるはずです」
languages.original_text: "I have a feeling that the palace is the anchor point of the enemy's raid. languages.text: “我的直觉告诉我，您的宫殿是敌军本次突袭的焦点。我们的音阵工程师侦测到，您的宫殿正在向外部发射某种未知信号。那群杂种肯定是在宫殿里设置了控制中心，只要拿下他们的指挥部，就能大大削弱外围部队的力量。”
languages.original_text: "I have a feeling that the palace is the anchor point of the enemy's raid. We take out their command — and we'll weaken their peripheral forces."

languages.text: «Tengo la impresión de que el palacio es el centro neurálgico del ataque enemigo. Nuestros ingenieros de vocos detectan transmisiones desde su residencia a las otras zonas del planeta. Esa chusma debe de haber establecido un centro de mando dentro. Si acabamos con sus líderes, debilitaremos a las fuerzas periféricas».
languages.original_text: "I have a feeling that the palace is the anchor point of the enemy's raid. We take out their command — and we'll weaken their peripheral forces."

languages.text: « J'ai l'impression que le palais est le centre névralgique du raid ennemi. Nos ingénieurs-vox ont intercepté des signaux inconnus, transmis de votre résidence vers d'autres zones de la planète. Ces pourritures ont dû établir un poste de communication. Si nous parvenons à détruire leur commandement, nous affaiblirons leurs forces secondaires. »
languages.original_text: "I have a feeling that the palace is the anchor point of the enemy's raid. We take out their command — and we'll weaken their peripheral forces."

languages.text: "Ich habe das Gefühl, der Palast ist das Hauptziel des feindlichen Überfalls. Unsere Vox-Ingenieure registrieren unbekannte Signale aus Eurer Residenz an andere Gebiete auf dem Planeten – dieser Abschaum muss im Inneren eine Steuerungszentrale eingerichtet haben. Wenn wir die ausschalten, schwächen wir auch ihre Truppen in anderen Bereichen."

languages.text: "İçimden bir ses, sarayın düşman istilasının başlangıç noktası olduğunu söylüyor. Voks mühendislerimiz, sarayınızdan gezegenin diğer bölgelerine bilinmeyen sinyaller gönderildiğini kayda geçti. Adiler içeride kontrol merkezi kurmuş olmalı. Komutayı devre dışı bırakabilirsek dış savunma kuvvetlerini de zayıflatırız."
languages.original_text: "I have a feeling that the palace is the anchor point of the enemy's raid. Our vox engineers are registering unknown signals coming from your residence to other areas on the planet — the scum must have set up a control centre inside. We take out their command — and we'll weaken their peripheral forces."

traits.locale_text: "İçimden bir his, sarayın düşman istilası için bir çapa görevi gördüğünü söylüyor. Voks mühendislerimiz, sarayınızdan gezegenin diğer bölgelerine giden sinyaller algıladı. Adiler içeride bir kontrol merkezi kurmuş olmalı. Komutalarını devre dışı bırakabilirsek yan kuvvetlerini de zayıflatırız."
